channel.title: Animal Park
channel.desc: There have been many successful newborns at the park over the years, but breeding programmes are not always easy. There's a race to stop one of the park's most important breeding programmes from falling apart. Last year, the park joined a red squirrel breeding programme, and they have already had babies. However, those babies are already nearly adults, they're squabbling, and they can't live together.
